songs.title: Zamo Zamo
songs.lyrics:
[Hook: Phyno]
Baby you hold me for work o
Make I enter your life I go love you better o
Nwa baby cool your temper oh
If na money or body you want I surrender o

[Chorus: Phyno & Wande Coal]
Zamo Zamo
Girl i want your loving
Zamo Zamo
Zamo Zamo
If I call you early in the morning
Make you Zamo Zamo
Zamo Zamo

So gi na Ku my heart beat

Gosi mu ezigbo colour GI ka pure white
Before mu a turnu onye olu to a house wife
Nwa as long as you gat me, baby I nwero shekin
Any man ga chu gi kwa ya you’re already taken
Eme foundation ewelu nwayo nwayo wuba dekin
Nwa afo no GI nwa bu my pino pino in the making
Oge mu no for you for your love i go sign undertaking

Baby you hold me for work o

Answer Answer

Odinaka
Odi di naka

Afigi naya
Odinaka
Odi di naka
Ifunaya

Nna f’ya, nwa o gejezu gi aru

(Eheee oge erugo to to) I na fu ya

Odinaka Make you Zamo Zamo Zamo Zamo Zamo Zamo Zamo Zamo
